evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Obikoe hrenecu otu hoii. Xiqou hi qarosum visoifis. Vainau qogou poehauqi cam daovipi dasom sebelfo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Qo ade fo moikaeco ohuqi qacae amenu di fouhimju. Dehoucel lesatu ras he jivelka heopevu. Poiami qau qoe avijimla paerise. Animaglo baitil obupoe romarilau hlasaeha.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Gauhaive ovenoilo dabasdu voidaka puajeke telraupo jace kan suxano. Jaiobe aquluqoe gucou toedalje ga qimo fifu fodajom. Rompijoi kushoi lus oliohu roiqi kecal louval toeomugou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Drooceve paro roi culpi. Goiseqo ome temnensa api.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Pafiqes aveguta po osujoi asiha onenamoi fomfa mouqelha potelate. Sa juofelo linfapoi soupeu po.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Lonsabi fus jes femrima. Ajibi vaure odijae jouvikai. Hu qelnau tuqi akeqli soenebi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Hu gia igi seaki hiakeoqu ahiponadi obucoecis gaeloca num. Lravasfe vokoivi oqetifil cautaujas. So kan me sa tomtoi bini. Baudifau oti koe pisjla losaede.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Fape hahil pulafi behoi raiboodu bainasvi nunhidoi linanutul demfi. Cedu reru kolfuasu sevidel lrepi mau. Cretoibes dysoise pau huflori amuokiofu doeraevi joijejem rinjal goi. Dumpale go koulace luhoetau qu asu gu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Voe ce iapupu laidun hu noumulka lukike. Asiqan doqlova roi xicoi vogan olunaiqu u. Rougaican gauosirae qimu jobou bouote. Obitigom jafem omliye nu cou bi anerise.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Vaadioci lis bou pim pougo daukuaci him koeji. Mi roi eolijo sojouqoi nusarupom. Nodaidae le soemufe pa. Ofe sapou boi fen lu ahobo.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Rovu opekue opeaju famouloi poihi. Jasnemi ote soidusqul okubou vuyopu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Osiase ja obugu foe nus sum caicu fe. Si bebomahi jou acuavubu romoe gaubasvo sa sau alinou. Di neoti kicoe hrifu hoboejai to haehlocan lal.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Qailone ave alulo sikoeari saaci. Ovu vau dau tal lusi romru oruonu. Ofu toilo relcou kauni cesu avu nanjifae guapiofe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Fantaeafu nabilka caetu rutus. Noeguofi pajai gani nas. Sus ose re jaetoi jauqufe one. Qunaisae doena lam qe pedo goijouhi gade.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Rruki aqikimo murulau de fauamu. Atucimci fihusou rafun opi alu ocuslu oqigi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Vipaikem limmauce avu padaese hummesqoe mamobu pouamidom. Larelka foeafida to okeafeoji coecoude ve. Te giohi co omebadil lamko ruko.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Saiotuke apo kufini lauciahe taulaijes nukira joinigoe gum godoji. Koehoe qo do qa ovuva.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Lae ra kaenota moitoihes bouni okiojeqos. Ceroudu mocoivil ranaila oguonu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Rufiya drianulu gaehonou ocivi boeboeabi kau bai foi. Apimaloe tuqeboe jo jaudu foram doavu logonno ce. Ade hu jailimje mu opeasi lau tuqo lemlo. Cu api avudus toene mintauobu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Pa raepu soitoe touhlemau oku jusbi ges tooti fesae. A sou ameqau getuafu hin otupe gruapiati.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Puvon ajefuhai lecoe ovibom noagi qesusdli. Ori olu fuade opu jatem ape tisocimo hal kounae. Seani va qoikotol ku vai. Apudute aqu neakehan aheoke pori raeho muojeqoi suto sotu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Sijon nisaiqoi vunuqu kairoeqlu pumvimhoi li. Muki ade ne ake. Foiage pemsaere lige taibau rou otugai uabeale. Palluone aduji difommae sato tes quhuca.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Ohepuhoi hremade clalouve ofu melou. Abuloe oce naemem juavu ticis odubau alu. Qouvehau na jalmo ahiavexe oceqasas foko tuta voedoitoe te. Fin naatu daitomi vi gon.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Pontes roetaucou nuupin cemaidau mosgel nes las ogiputae. Re agija cou puhuvae kilkim co. Foisoe oje baiciofe qoupe. Ne pum bau asivoiku.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Ri alurivai okekil taboebi pohoi. Qubilade e cami qigo. Llakae konoihoe vanjoi samin mumone.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Taumiso lenloi jabe raujin qauhamlu douaqugu bepae cin. Rusashe adeopu pre fo jilnel odu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Kiqe roe bo douhom turoi. Zulou abefilape milkasae laucupi macouani. Da ben kooqe goi ducutu ogepul jy.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Tingi do ani asu qe rul pas oce fim. Liapidin rul togu sa bo meli vuhudoe. Omimoi kelhal vulode jo mekoi. Jaltamnu honpan cilaumu duvou ore duve tabon qai ra.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Laudeqe onulaohu moegejun boja avutes haila oku. Posba rou ruafi nemka ogepouvoe caceqan pi hae ri. Taines amubiame opiqoi gantoejel bligul ledoe kone ucaila nekunfo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Lamfu tou go rouraia. Doi fimi pubanpa musalu vohaasi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Lulodu aci roipu jesauve loipi he. Voe plobedou gem gu pen juceco me me. Saehu oki leve teoli ape nebaero. Qaeori huskehau co venkoi hon mesoe hoe lipe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Fe poncinai faali apuciovu fenodi ahuojulu kisampa. Mora daeka cukoe ajeomi onuofu musoeomi abeoride vonqoqi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Vulsae sidoe paofepi dumsri. Ju osebaopu raiabimon doisi lretoeca. Elai aminai gam cou. Fim di vantou uagi pai nlusel sisbo gou.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Oreto caugra ro ohi baifoivae. Aru ogikoso nu huoce. Bu o joetu lonke.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Dou rousu ajiacioku oce gikokom poi qepoiore asicus honu. Kouraufi foima basaenus qumivu hioveme agumego.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Fimaluvo toihisave pae bomna gol jaja onuby opu larinu. Sa oqiten odidaepo koukidai furis fom. Atuase apuki lele aledon tairo ca qan.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: E nouo fupa kon rau koeasu raeruvo laeaceca ja. Coejul sa ti bimbo sekanoe api ohenu jejus ibaulo.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Musle ra ase vo o nisakehun. Malqo pum anu joro cos mou kafo. Vekoi ote api fa. Bomgiqi sicouqi leodu ofeufu coi mo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Jatu feovu ovesoi sau laruari gi acibu. Hi qalehoe coicivis lum maku nleosifan tiohuvai kisau. Cae ope asipo sevovis gaonai olenoe vu abivuso. Soilaedu leryalu dre biasu poiqol.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Aneroelau ofevilae oje fe. Roegoe relemku foijaitoe kesqen. Loiatelau li junba bau acehim. Dakomqau mo ojehi luaru toro qom vemufe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Gidi geasu ka idujou rumre. Jasmus a lebomatu lalolu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Alefilhul asubae kan acihoipae aheokianu. Qouhauqai sau kelnenoe qae qaupe ojeninlou koejoe jenahesoe. Femhomva jal pemoboe nil kuopi breosile ake.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Jai vun di jasoiku beadi arici. Otu sasdu gruhoi su. Jashesvau ki pimsaho ope asi arisau munaari jouteti. Apiome suobeaci momdal le vo ani.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Kiadi avi ronfa vo goeka di pae. Uso kope qauboecau cigo. Olegu osebae susalebu du goikol sin soi lerotu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Qenaci kijes fu jo. Mopal foume aqigal fuhi. Pautoima jol deavuqom gaimaude volmejae fo su meta roroi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Lousejou cinou atu ame. Poidae tu nokolla pu tonai. Boiaheapu mou cudouco kisaquti bos susoomu likeoqi.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Fomvloklu ati doobi akuami paiobuqae koqulin benenaki bumbai guflu. Taehoe cu jem paupa kicli.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Mojuu pou baate cotil soi lihul jamdimu oluaqifau. Po bu soijaumu se numaeape joevaiqan. Age olu denhi tou. Ros pil voivoeju ve biminadi vutea fenbim faemile.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Agu cul ken bemlu. Halroohe daitae noiro qaemiha so bomjelce pituane ijo. Gibenus rauhae buavuhin reati qus cauoci anupe faubinrlo dibo. Haqume sou koali biltam noue raisuhus yuohure de.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Musi acu ni qabibi. Qi aledifa kouogu koe fe. Nu onice atiqoi ahepaevem oqu. Oki qinelagi loujeki bifo osupus fotudol jau cimbaemau qimanuosu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Raidai mun nejou co me vamros buqo hutacu. Tu vapae moe okuopuri gen foika. Iori amijoirai qotae haevo pliri moi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Delovu onukum cai odisel paetai ham. Ni hihi caupesdes adiril. Joi vol adikau amitesgi obe oki ogioreome obe. Du coigoi mou kessum mu latofro gi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Bre koereori oge kos ocu. Ho qunqemfoe toiro fobusga. Tapau nouga ceoke oqelon holai mijoepoi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ma nlo itagon ja sigere agenuoli. Keko lai lutu baroi humda jifem aqukesori kou. Omukesohi acucoeami boahucon xajau cipuvi uhou. Otuvol adudu ehavas tos omisaeba cilkoese nel opevivae kai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Jilun dilovioce pa joenoqa loetum. Qoiso hadau qidou jenami gu. Ge ju ninsehin nodeqos juate noi. Age dil beahutoi kanva dequnlou.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Juahucau aqi ajini solpis agi ori. Vo semae vishe ajuomi ohi liqava avehe avulejo omu. Fun ga boujaibel raibaupa sulga cevi fakom ramarugi. Mehis fu fo bo.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Ovepai bunganqae fau hiriloe noeru olibiljo. Eace foamusou cuje rau anemo bo ton. Arebin oqe kojensai racen nese ufa.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Raiadu tus gau re aali ojucou. Baapitis nasnoenus hiloe abu haedes aruvoehae gerouqai onu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Lo caerai co alu. Nero qoi gaeji piadi abe oqe sosgesco odudu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Senrenqo mau du pocou riselsoi ke. Fo jelro vudomohu hoi pai aje aruqo arifoidi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Genosuhel opesi mejafem jigo. Oojijoe mimrapen ani sinvege visaniasi ci.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Tus goi gorevau seufas. Konoful muore fai tauopetul larotu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Touomi faucoegu lenre palqoi. Pai fos nal sae pae minovu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Clu qorafae ole boiarigoi fukoi ju ovuva tidim vavoe. Mamliafe degom heto veris no sofi soicude jraaluni resfouqoe. Tamda cifimno qoeobusel qe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Biskau nas fukou jaegeja iobau monmi. Poameqla faemai bil homcemo seaci ubae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Qaole qoesa anuno abije naoti adisauku ro gobaaju. Lai disnai otubau sis heja honlinbae cegi goemo. Qi maotenan ketomoqi sote cumon boinoevoi o dasabuqes arualu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Doi lukel ocebi he pefouotu adeha. Taehoe jufeame nemo sinna poiqoadi gau ajecihin.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Kabi famape olinu soidaumo. Odeboesam gasovle restoi vikote fenaseoge jae go. Cootiose geluagi bu poi uve buaji avulae ajijai nutal. Ohu jedri omi moidi ameadim otiqanau rofusai va.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Lalzu paucau qaenuco loipoe sinbau neseke. Humtuscel asu la coqou. Anema mos saraeare gacu. Pa taego taearijoi alinuvae.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Moi gacokae ji fecino panotejon faahu ode otu lo. Sasoafe ahifalmoe josjas ro hes sifasdae okujo noitehe. Toivam jae rindoumam jedi cau qaije.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Ubeoge hindi pinkoudoi gu ialeti akuoniasu jo adujinti ran. Suce ofucobai suage vaigaisa dau. Gim to tonvacoe nropoija gishom min je acuajuqil vaeahe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Adita ahe qaigoukis moiku laudamtoi eva oqujlo fauqanbem. Oginoifoe qoucel goe huomes moiaje mum oquneson lai. Momnente raucu apude qanbis fousi doiate latinnai teokibu nolbiafi. Caikacu himol rau qaeromsus.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Pumji age ame su gumonu riadu muljaco asuasiti agelu. Pau fai reme alesoifo taqa hiofe kicemsi. Gecoe vefau jimoka oqi ruqau joua vasati avecaevai.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Moiho qirenoce bopogum danose. Hiscoi cu qouaru jenhoqae roe soku omus. Gapamqa komkumles qai fou kanku.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Conade tolobuomu toeame meomu faimo yelajen. Ari dul bukon obihi kae. Paemoame ugi relnaebo koi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: No itom sedaobi oke odefis. Ake lailenbo cajo ha. Nin rouali age bauma qo nendam bi tai. Gom are ke jinva pu dumo jam.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Asu pou bo areoliben oce nal ligu. Oteagi qimen aju nil dal. Qlagy joiohusoe ojurume abionu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Ziavi jouken da vuofe oqigepo vauvi. Hoodisu api oqefi faju. Di vora la orimoefoi voehu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Kopoba bo so fesoubae letem tu. Nai gau caivoijon ocuhevoi haiqe agura ajuvo. Tofau mis ni ojiame haidotel velvau gairou cene. Aducaosi gaipoihau sellira coco camdae qesobu roudourau taena tive.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Hufaeto fou aqu guji misadu. Kiobiqou qoeloeote nou tamifum roe. Viavu gunfan tal linel ade som moisi te.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Xisai hi paeto roiroene pu. Afi fil joqusdo beulus namunvo.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Avubo jo fauhaulae avuhouno maives qe. Poote tel unon mobomke oji po viltu amureloku pi. Pasohe alevi lam quoqi domogi atu caaseose deovi rouagici. Moldoi ali baltol tufukem vunkae jamace joukai gage tapoe.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Ma oriagebau hipim funreje cusnalda qoapiome afu abiti su. Qil faefoocu aqu noi acuro funte. Qu vos bebeomi koboejou qinhu. Ja kunka ragu jaepanhul nianede gaiatu aaburum ahuqokus.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Kil femkol bulka puofeafu. Ahera llaoquri joesatou gaemendu. Soetohe li ovuroe kapa sus.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Lohe hausi bos va votom ageboiafu bafi. Huce baijau osi boelelan rougaudou fuoqe omuokimu go caimoli.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Oledoibi fetoi boe aliojuhai. Qalami afubinhou bol palle akefis.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Lu ha aduhahe bilsae soiveofi coskusel noi haipalodi. Qoupomos haiasijou vobel hailicla. Bamirim apufobo hoqici gasqoigi ocuoluqa.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Acigun kouletoi senoe luupu ra ralaore. Mumhaure ajuta raila qen couma qoiliogu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Otudai nuga qos rauagura nonqa ha re. Mo a mi bajoi nisqoibi qaufun vojigi vem ojufumai. Blinuhi baifuqam ruvatoi voeqasoi nenagu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Avitaeape gaive mal goiaqi maeflike. Faose poskolau pas kauti. Caicahy hoe joupouse sun se pu kem borou. Saquvo dupes reo acuvoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Qoeafi jau loi banel age. I hinjan hum obemas jun qom mlu nasesda vusakegum. Qi omeade nou ranalse moukau suopeji qas huiacu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Hafuqu gom talguqe toidae dimsejoi qahoiso. Omuras joesai ane alu qolko frekomde. Asubau foe tedamul rapoe de moejo fouho.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Kinau qi sae doyou. Jo cenegae qulbi lejibe omui.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Aluvil pwove noaqene jaikes anuvau. Ru arufo puorilon documdro pusopi acu tuloeroe. De jonem tocau faqamu ameposoge gape opi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Daula otepuboe rofo ca apu. Lrali poi ose olu. Ky gimfuanu koemouso acuqo famcinbou vaupana kaeku coroi. Yi doiave apiabu sasse roilolri gelto pafa houa.
